Thursday, 05 September 2013

Show Description
................

From the Infowars web site :: On the Thursday, September 5 broadcast of The Alex Jones Show, Alex analyzes the steady beating of the war drums and why they will likely reach crescendo in a Syrian military strike, which will undoubtedly leave hundreds of innocents dead in its wake, unless independent media can alert enough people in time to prevent it. 

Alex also breaks down the latest attempt at propagandizing the American people through a fake Alyssa Milano sex tape, Russia's warning of a nuclear disaster should the US attack Syria and China's buildup of warships off the coast of Syria. 

On today's show, Alex welcomes Director of Gun Owners of America Larry Pratt to discuss Obama's recent gun control initiatives, which authorized the closing of a little-known gun-buying loophole and banned the re-importation of military surplus firearms.
